The instruction works only for minikube setup:

Execute the following commands:

sudo chmod +x ./install.sh
sudo ./install.sh  

Pass the:
1. Workspace for terraform
2. 'Tag' you want to use for the docker image.
3. The 'release name' for your helm application

After the script execution you can also  access the website with the following URL  ---> trazler.info:<port-number-given-by-minikube>

To destroy:

cd terraform 
terraform destroy -auto-approve